post.description:
创建 PPT 合并会话

Request: FormData with ppt_a and ppt_b files

Response:
{
    "session_id": "abc12345",
    "documents": {
        "ppt_a": {"source_file": "...", "total_slides": 5},
        "ppt_b": {"source_file": "...", "total_slides": 8}
    }
}

恢复历史版本

Request:
{
    "session_id": "abc12345",
    "document_id": "ppt_a",
    "slide_index": 1,
    "target_version": "v1"
}

Response:
{
    "success": true,
    "current_version": "v1"
}

删除/恢复页面

Request:
{
    "session_id": "abc12345",
    "document_id": "ppt_a",
    "slide_index": 2,
    "action": "delete"
}

Response:
{
    "success": true,
    "status": "deleted"
}

get.description:
获取会话详情（包含所有文档的完整版本历史）

Response:
{
    "session_id": "abc12345",
    "documents": {
        "ppt_a": {
            "source_file": "...",
            "slides": {
                "0": {
                    "current_version": "v1",
                    "status": "active",
                    "versions": [
                        {"version": "v1", "image_url": "...", "operation": "原始上传"}
                    ]
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

获取指定页面的版本历史

Response:
{
    "versions": [
        {"version": "v1", "image_url": "...", "operation": "原始上传"},
        {"version": "v2", "image_url": "...", "operation": "ai_polish", "prompt": "..."}
    ]
}
